/**
 * @defgroup dynamic_buffer_stream_unit_tests dynamic_buffer_stream unit tests
 * @ingroup dynamic_buffer_stream_tests_group
 *
 * @brief Unit tests for the `dynamic_buffer_stream` adapter.
 *
 * @details
 * The tests in this group verify the contracts of:
 * - `dynamic_buffer_stream_default_cfg()`
 * - `dynamic_buffer_stream_default_env()`
 * - `dynamic_buffer_stream_create_stream()`
 * - `dynamic_buffer_stream_create_desc()`
 * - descriptor constructor usage through `stream_adapter_desc_t::ctor`
 *
 * The tests in this group also verify the behavior of the adapter private
 * callbacks:
 * - `dynamic_buffer_stream_write()`
 * - `dynamic_buffer_stream_read()`
 * - `dynamic_buffer_stream_flush()`
 * - `dynamic_buffer_stream_close()`
 *
 * These private callbacks are exercised through the public `stream` API and
 * lifecycle entry points rather than being called directly.
 */